<p><span class="anchor" id="p25"></span><span class="c2">(١٢١٢ - ١٢٥٩ هـ)</span> <span class="c2">(١٧٩٧ - ١٨٤٣ م)</span><a href="#p25" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
